creator: Ammar Rosli
descriptionHtml:
Explore Wayang, a new way to discover resources and information on movies to watch in Brunei cinemas.

Features include:
• Movie info, trailers and showtimes for currently showing movies as well as upcoming ones
• Rate and share your thoughts of movies that you have watched (coming soon!)
• Add movie showtimes to your calendar as well as make bookings and calls to the cinemas
• Ticket prices for all cinemas
• Locate nearest local cinemas to your location
• Share movies to watch with family and friends
• Universal app that works beautifully on tablet

Supported cinemas:
• Aman Hills Cineplex
• One Cineplex
• The Arena Cineplex
• The Grand Stand Cinema
• The Mall Cineplex
• Times Cineplex (Times Square, Empire, Tutong and Kuala Belait)

Love the app? Rate us! Your feedback is essential to make the app even better. Be sure to follow @wayangapp on Twitter for updates. Thanks for using Wayang!
